WEBVTT

00:08:29.727 --> 00:08:32.010
Memandangkan Nelson meninggal 
tiga bulan lepas,

00:08:32.034 --> 00:08:34.620
saya fikir keadaan 
kesihatannya cukup parah."

00:08:34.644 --> 00:08:37.458
(Ketawa)

00:08:37.482 --> 00:08:41.001
Itulah keadaan kesihatan 
yang paling teruk, tidak hidup.

00:08:43.373 --> 00:08:46.354
Dia kata, "SILA PATUH 
ARAHAN JURUBANK SAYA.

00:08:46.354 --> 00:08:47.546
SATU CINTA."

00:08:47.546 --> 00:08:49.302
(Ketawa)

00:08:50.325 --> 00:08:52.983
Saya kata, "Tentulah. 
TIADA WANITA, TIADA TANGISAN."

00:08:52.983 --> 00:08:55.671
(Ketawa)

00:08:55.695 --> 00:08:59.191
(Tepukan)